    "LLMs are continually being refined, and so is their performance.",
    "To conclude, LLMs hold potential for breast cancer management, especially in text analysis and guideline-driven question-answering.",
    "Yet, their inconsistent accuracy warrants cautious use, following thorough validation and ongoing supervision.",
    "Lukac et al.",
    "2023 07.2023 Evaluating ChatGPT as an adjunct for the multidisciplinary tumor board decision-making in primary breast cancer cases Archives of Gynecology and Obstetrics Haver et al."
